CBRE are pleased to present 35 Harrington Street, Arundel for lease. This modern industrial facility is located approximately 5 minutes from the M1 Motorway between Westfield Helensvale and Harbour Town Shopping Centre.  With a clearspan warehouse and modern office facilities this is the ideal building for any business looking to upgrade. 

The property features:
- 1,560sqm of high clearance warehousing
- 356sqm of high quality office
- Total building area of 1,971sqm 
- Total land area of 3,419sqm  
- 3 on-grade electric roller doors 
- 27 onsite car parks
- Large awning over roller doors
- Corporate office facility with excellent natural light
- Multiple under cover car parks

For further information on this excellent opportunity contact your marketing agents today.

CBRE is please to present the Gold Coast premier industrial located of Captain Cook Drive, Arundel. 

The estate provides businesses with easy access to major arterial roads including the Gold Coast Highway, Smith Street and is a short distance to the M1 Motorway connecting Brisbane to Northern New South Wales. 

Gold Coast Logistics Hub Features: 

- Leasing opportunities from 2,000, 5,000, 10,000 and up to 30,000sqm* available
- B-Double approved route from Brisbane Road 
- Zoned Medium Impact Business 
- Approved for 24/7 operations. 
- Home to Toll Logistics and other major industrial users. 

If you’re a large manufacturing, logistics or warehousing business who requires a facility over 2,000sqm and up to 30,000sqm then this estate is a must see. 

Contact your exclusive agents today to discuss further.
